description: Ruhland’s Strudel Haus is a maker of fabulous sweet and savory strudel.  Inspired by the belief that food is a celebration and is integrated in our relationship with ourselves, with the Earth and with one another.  Their hope is that the food they create will gather people around the table to celebrate the love and community found in family and friends.  Find Ruhland's Strudel Haus in Minneapolis, Minnesota!
name: Ruhland's Strudel Haus
